Achievements.Name: Extreme challenge
Achievements.Description: Finish the Campaign on Elite (unlocks achievements for Normal and Hard, if not earned).

Achievements.Name: TDM rookie
Achievements.Description: Win a Team Deathmatch game.

Achievements.Name: Support ace
Achievements.Description: Call in every support element at least once.

Achievements.Name: Cannon ace
Achievements.Description: Destroy 50 enemies with the cannon in multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Joint Strike missile ace
Achievements.Description: Score 135 kills with Joint Strike missiles in multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Multi Target AA missile ace
Achievements.Description: Score 100 kills with Multi Target AA missiles in multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Radar-Guided missile ace
Achievements.Description: Score 75 kills with Radar Guided missiles in multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: All Aspect missile ace

Achievements.Name: Deflector ace
Achievements.Description: Deflect 150 missiles from friendly planes.

Achievements.Name: Wing ace pilot
Achievements.Description: Remain the Team Ace for a total time of 20 minutes.

Achievements.Name: Versatile pilot
Achievements.Description: Obtain an end-match award 20 times.

Achievements.Name: Christine
Achievements.Description: Kill 100 opponents using the same plane in multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Gladiator
Achievements.Description: Participate in 100 Team Deathmatch games.

Achievements.Name: Not safe enough
Achievements.Description: Kill an enemy with a missile while being jammed in a multiplayer match.

Achievements.Name: Ambush!
Achievements.Description: Score a cannon kill while having Radar Suppression active in a multiplayer match.

Achievements.Name: Medic
Achievements.Description: Repair 90 hp by using a single Repair Drone support

Achievements.Name: Unimpressed
Achievements.Description: Score a kill with the Cannon while the enemy has Missile Suppression active.

Achievements.Name: Avoidance ace

Achievements.Name: Counter support ace
Achievements.Description: Complete all counter support challenges.

Achievements.Name: Predator

Achievements.Name: Veteran
Achievements.Description: Win 25 Team Deathmatch games.

Achievements.Name: Sitting ducks

Achievements.Name: Point blank shot

Achievements.Name: Test pilot
Achievements.Description: Play Team Deathmatch games using 30 different planes.

Achievements.Name: Risky stuff
Achievements.Description: Recover from stall at an altitude of 30 meters or lower in Team Deathmatch.

Achievements.Name: Evasion ace
Achievements.Description: Dodge 10 Radar-Guided missiles without using flares in multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Wing leader
Achievements.Description: Be the Match Leader for a total time of 20 minutes.
